headline: Reflecting On Shelf-Stable Food Stocks’ Q1 Earnings: Campbell's (NASDAQ:CPB)
summary: The end of the earnings season is always a good time to take a step back and see who shined (and who not so much). Let’s take a look at how shelf-stable food stocks fared in Q1, starting with Campbell's (NASDAQ:CPB).
